column8: Synthetic sole
獲獎 - 專為在技術地形上無與倫比的表現而設計，La Sportiva's Bushido 越野跑鞋已獲得《 Trail Runner 》雜誌的編輯精選獎。
重量輕 - 低調設計僅重 10.50 盎司 (298 公克)，適合長程路跑；STB 控制結構採用足底包覆的 TPU 框架，提供最大的穩定性和反應能力，而沒有額外重量。
高性能保護 - 外底齒紋有圓滑的邊緣和中底重疊，以增加摩擦力並增強在外傾地形上的穩定性；前腳採用雙密度壓縮 EVA rock guard/TPU 鞋板有助預防挫傷。
透氣 - AirMesh 鞋面、側網眼襯墊和 Stretch AirMesh 鞋舌一起作用，保持雙腳乾爽，有助防止起泡；內部套入式結構如襪子般貼合腳部，不會造成過度壓力。
穩定性和控制 - 雙密度 FriXion XT V 溝槽與衝擊煞車系統提供優異的穩定性，適用於急速下降、光滑的小路；使用敏捷的黏性橡膠鞋底，自信地跨越岩石、屋頂和其他障礙物。"

âœ” 輕量及吸濕內底 ---- 全網布慢跑鞋的重量輕盈，為您帶來無比柔軟棉的穿著感受，讓您變成快速移動的豹。 此外，吸濕排汗鞋墊有助於保持雙腳在運動時涼爽舒適。
âœ” SHOCKPROOF & NON-SLIP SOLE ---- 這些越野跑鞋外底採用 EVA 彈性泡沫製成，完美符合 S 形的機械原則，增加減震效果。 此外，由於特殊 RB 材質的協助，這些鞋子非常耐用，而且防滑。
♣ 容易穿 ---- 鞋舌和鞋跟的輕盈運動鞋都配有堅固的皮帶，主要能比其他正常運動鞋減少穿著和脫鞋。 此外，這些皮帶美化您的鞋子，讓它們看起來相當酷和特別，而不是豐富。 ​"

column8: 【防滑鞋頭與防震】：休閒步行鞋的外腳趾部分與鞋底由耐用 PU 皮革製成，厚層橡膠與塑膠製成。 它具有耐磨性和抗皺性，能夠抵抗硬物，同時保持腳趾形狀，並在走路時獲得反彈和緩衝效果。 結合 Ortholite 鞋墊的相同特性，可改善持久舒適的踏板感受，緩解腳部疲勞。
【透氣性】：運動慢跑鞋使用 Fly-knit 網眼，可作為鞋面底層和鞋面的彈性繫帶，可吸濕排汗，形成雙腳；鞋墊網眼襯裡讓鞋子透氣性更佳，並提供涼爽舒適的穿著環境。

column8: Lug Sole sole
All the fun, freedom, and benefits of being barefoot, but with the protection and comfort you want in a sport sandal. Xero Shoes come with our 5,000 mile warranty.
Perfect if you hike, walk, run, jog, work out, Crossfit, yoga, raft, stand up paddle board, kayak, canoe, fly fish, even run ultra-marathons.
Up to 70% lighter than other sport sandals. Only 5.5mm thick, it's perfect for travel. Flexible enough to roll up and fit in your pack or pocket. Durable enough for wherever the Z-Trek takes you.

Zero-drop non-elevated heel for natural posture. 5.5mm non-marking FeelTrue sole. Water resistant. Fast-drying. Great grip and traction. Z-style webbing holds securely, yet slides on and off in seconds.

NOTE: For the best chance of a correct fit, please measure your foot: 1) Place a piece of paper on the floor, against a wall; 2) Step on the paper, your heel against the wall; 3) Mark the paper in line with your longest toe; 4) Measure that length with a ruler; 5) Compare that length to the sizing chart (link, above). To REALLY ensure a correct fit, get printable templates of the exact sizes by contacting the Seller."

column8: Ultraventity是亞軍世界編輯選擇獎得主，是我們最緩震的步道跑鞋，靈感來自我們的步道和超棒。
我們的 30 公釐 x 25 公釐堆疊高度和 5 公釐墜落採用 3 件式、多密度 EVA 中底，可在步態週期中提供光導。
積極的 Vibram XS Trek 外底在技術路徑上提供牽引力、耐用性和保護。 全襯墊的舌頭和耐磨工程網眼鞋面經過優化，以提高透氣性和強度，並具有排水端口，用於釋放水和更快乾燥。
5 公釐抗微生物矯形鞋墊可抵禦壓縮組和氣味，獨特貼合的步態附件使其完全兼容我們的拉伸尼龍Topo gaiter（可選並另售）。"

column8: ADVANCED TECHNOLOGY: Columbia Men's Alpine FTG Outdry Trail Running Shoe is crafted of our signature waterproof and breathable construction to help keep you dry and comfortable.

WIDE TOE BOX DESIGN - Wide enough toe box allows your toes to relax and spread out naturally for more comfort and stability in uphill climbs and downhill descents, helping with balance and giving you better feedback from the ground

ANTI-SLIP SOLE & ANTI-COLLISION TOE CAP - Rubber outsole offer the optimal balance of traction and durability. The toe cap of the booties with protective structure enhance the protection of your feet

MULTIPLE USES - These minimalist cross training shoes are suitable for casual walking, running, training, hiking, gym, pilates, jogging, biking, climbing, camping, yoga, driving, vacation etc. You can also wear it as a water shoes"

column8: 【FLYKNIT TECHNIQUE】這款迷彩皇冠時尚步行鞋的飛行針織鞋面提供絕佳的包覆和平衡應力，輕輕地擁抱移動的腳並提升運動表現。
【透氣網布】這些慢跑鞋的兩側都配有尼龍氣孔，使內部空氣隨機流出。 有助於保持舒適的溫度和濕度，有效讓您的雙腳在移動時感到涼爽。
【輕盈鞋身】輕盈的 MD 外側材質搭配飛織網眼鞋面，彈性足以讓您的雙腳感到舒適。 側面通風孔可讓您穿著這些休閒跑步運動鞋，享受愉快的涼爽。
【防震技術】這些透氣鞋的 MD 中底是緩衝的來源。 鞋底深溝提供更多寬腳空間，加強反彈效果，緩解壓力，保護膝蓋和骨頭。
【絕佳的牽引力】鞋底延伸器與 TPR 道路固定組件相匹配。 根據運動技師，TRP 零件以科學方式分散，以改善快速跑步的牽引力。 穿上這些輕盈的網球鞋，出去尋找運動樂趣！"

column8: Rubber sole
WELL CUSHIONED - The Mutant packs a whole lot of cushion in an aggressive yet ultralight package, making it durable mountain running shoe ideal for moderate to technical terrain

FIGHTS FRICTION - Integrated Fusiongate Lacing Harness with High Frequency reinforcements and Spyraltongue technology pair up to deliver a snug, stay-put fit that reduces friction and maintains comfort for high mileage trail running

LIGHTWEIGHT, BREATHABLE - AirMesh fabric keeps your feet cool on hot days, controls moisture and prevents blisters without adding unnecessary weight; 4-way stretch dynamic scree guard protects ultralight uppers from loose rock
STABILITY & CONTROL - Super grippy FriXion XF sole with Impact Brake System and V-Groove provides excellent traction and stability on slick trails and uneven ground, allowing you to stop on a dime

AWARD-WINNING - Designed for unbeatable performance on technical terrain, La Sportiva’s Mutant Trail Running Shoe has earned the Editors’ Choice award from Trail Runner and the Gear of the Year title from Outside Magazine"

column8: Lightweight & Non-slip : Brand new upgraded rubber sole delivers flexibility and reliable traction on wet surfaces. Our shoes are great in appearance and light in foot. Your feet are free to move.

Easy on and off : The pull tab of the heel helps to quickly put on and take off. The elastic speed lace system allows you to adjust the tightness easily, which avoid the trouble caused by tying normal laces.

Soft & Durable : Our barefoot shoes can be easily folded. You can put it in your bag when you go out or after using it. It won’t take up too much space. Meanwhile, skin-friendly inner material won’t rub your feet and make these shoes wearable enough to do any sports.

Zero heel-to-toe drop allows the feet to be in a neutral position which supports a healthy posture and puts less stress on the joints. Ideal for any activities, such as hiking, jogging, gym, walking, surfing, sailing, boating, yoga and so on."

多功能：適合水上公園、劃船、衝浪、沙灘排球、普拉提、重量訓練、尾翼、帆船、帆板、帆船、帆板運動、帆板運動、帆板運動、帆板運動、騎自行車慢跑、跑步、釣魚、花園、草坪、Equestrian、籃球、運動員、手球、拳擊、桌網球、藝術表演、沙灘排球。 Amphibious 鞋款，可讓您在陸地或水中享受生活。
一雙合身的多功能水鞋 能為您的生活帶來更多樂趣。 請根據您實際腳長選擇正確的尺寸。"

舒適 - 我們的中底緩衝是由多層組成，以保護戰術戰士。 我們以雙密度 EVA 中底開始；鞋跟稍微柔軟，增加坐墊和彈性。 我們在底部嵌入全長 Rock 'n Roll PlateTM 以防止從岩石和屋頂刷傷。 strobel 鞋垫板带有一层 EVA 衬里，额外缓冲。
OUTPREFORM - 鞋面有許多功能在今天大多數越野跑者找不到。 模製橡膠鞋頭可在門內踢腳時協助並保護 足部。 注塑成型的 TPU 鞋跟夾增加了支撐力，並提供卓越的穩定性。 我們構造鞋面以提供最大透氣性。 使用最好的超細纖維 PU 以及透氣的尼龍網布，這樣的方式來促進優越的空氣流量，因此，更健康的腳部環境。
TACTICAL - 坚固的越野跑步者拥有战术特点，始于 Altama 传奇的 Panama 鞋底技术。 使用粘性 SOF-ROCTM 橡膠，在足弓上包覆，幫助快速旋轉，我們已經將典型的跑道變成戰術機器！
您追求的品質 - 尼龍環繫帶系統有助於快速調整。 在鞋跟上，你會發現一個尼龍拉環，以幫助當你穿上鞋子的時候。 在腳跟上，你會發現一個尼龍拉環。 我們的內底是 Alta-liteTM 雙密度吹 PU 內底，提供卓越的緩衝和支撐。
SINCE 1969 - Altama 一直是 Mil-Spec 靴子美國防衛部的領導製造商，為全球供應軍事人員"

column8: MADE FOR THE OUTDOORS - Our Men’s Trail Running Shoes work fantastically for all terrains, but were made specifically for the outdoors! With our special trail-specific outsole with reversed traction lugs, you can run with confidence knowing that your feet are planted firmly on the ground. No slipping and sliding with Steel Edge!

FULL SUPPORT FOR YOUR FEET - Our molded EVA midsole guarantees support all over your feet to ensure full foot reinforcement! The molded midsole will keep your underfoot structured, as well as your arches happy and healthy! No more worrying about how striking the ground will affect your feet, Steel Edge guarantees a painless jog!

VERSATILITY - Steel Edge Men’s Trail Running Shoe comes with a removable sock liner, for step-in comfort and superior cushioning! Easily removable, Steel Edge guarantee that you will have no issue inserting your own customized sock liner for your personalized foot comfort, whatever your specific podiatric needs are.

LUXURIOUS LEATHER - With the highest quality workmanship, you can always trust Steel Edge, and our top-notch leather is guaranteed to satisfy! Our smooth leather, and it’s comforting texture will enhance your running experience, keeping your feet in tip-top runners shape.

CUSTOMER SATISFACTION – We are always striving to provide the best quality shoes to our customers. However, if for various reason, you are dissatisfied with your purchase, simply send us back your unworn shoes, with original tags on and we will be happy to issue you a full refund or replacement."

『MD Outsole』 The cushion sock shoes with MD outsole has a good shock absorption, with air cushion design, can evenly distribute pressure, enhance flexibility and stability, protect your ankles, so you walk more safely

『Widely Occasion』 Cycling, Swimming, Boating, Camping, Beach, Driving, Walking Shoes offer a fashion casual look that is ideal for everyday wear"

column1: B07P879XWW,Salming,https://www.amazon.com/Salming-Trail-Sports-Outdoor-Running/dp/B07P879XWW/ref=sr_1_639?pf_rd_i=16225019011&pf_rd_m=ATVPDKIKX0DER&pf_rd_p=a8717793-9e88-48bb-b385-3487bae57557&pf_rd_r=A0Y4T1VK1Z4K6VG1HJJN&pf_rd_s=merchandised-search-left-2&pf_rd_t=101&qid=1569436271&rnid=679286011&s=fashion-mens-intl-ship&sr=1-639,"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/419Z9BpmM8L._AC_US40_.jpg,https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/41VsFdkl0YL._AC_US40_.jpg,https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/41sLP%2Bj8xYL._AC_US40_.jpg,https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/31KHdT8dazL._AC_US40_.jpg,https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/41sSrkIW0KL._AC_US40_.jpg,https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/G/01/x-locale/common/transparent-pixel._V192234675_.gif",Salming Men's Trail 5 Sports Outdoor Running Shoes,,,,,"TWD 4,745.26","TWD 9,035.80","3 LAYER CONSTRUCTION: A first layer of mesh material adds comfort, while the middle stabilizes lateral movements and reduces pressure on the foot. The exterior thin net mesh encapsulates and wraps up the front in a neat fashion, adding durability to the shoe.

column8: EXO SKELETON: The Exo Skeleton stabilizes the foot in lateral movements and relieves pressure at the MTP joints. It eliminates friction and reduces the impact of the side forces in the soft parts of the foot, especially underneath the forefoot.
ROOMY TOE BOX: The toe box is more roomy in order to provide a possibility for the fore foot to expand properly in the landing phase, making it more effective in a biomechanic perspective.
RECOIL MIDSOLE: The material in the midsole is RECOIL compound - which is a super lightweight cushioning compound that releases a high rebound energy effect.
TORSION EFFICIENCY UNIT: The Torsion Efficiency Unit brings sturdiness to the shoe. It is appropriately placed to generate maximal running efficiency."

column8: 輕薄、運動風格：乾淨、苗條的鞋面，細節細緻，幾乎適合任何冬季服裝或情況

column8: 精確腳掌：穿上這雙鞋，在最具挑戰性的風景中提供精確的節奏，Endofit 和 Sensifit 為您提供最佳的腳掌，而不會犧牲舒適度。
彈性舒適：Techno 布料以防風雨的 GORE-TEX 鞋款符合技術地形，可呼吸並保護，讓您度過所有季節。

column8: WELL CUSHIONED - The Mutant 以永續但超輕的包裝包裝提供大量靠枕，讓這款山地跑鞋更耐用，適合作為技術地形
FIGHTS 摩擦 - 集成 Fusiongate 繫帶帶，具備高頻率強化和 Spyraltongue 技術配對，可提供緊密貼合，減少摩擦並保持舒適，以實現高哩程越野跑
輕盈、透氣 - AirMesh 布料讓雙腳在炎熱天氣中保持涼爽，控制水分並防止氣泡，而不會增加不必要的重量；四向彈力動態網紗保護可保護超輕的鞋面，防止鬆散的搖滾
穩定性和控制 - 超抓地力 FriXion XF 鞋底，帶有衝擊煞車系統和 V-Groove，提供優異的牽引力和穩定性，滑行道和不均勻的地面，讓您可以停止在灰塵上
AWARD-WINNING - 專為技術地形上無與倫比的表現而設計，La Sportiva 的突變越野跑鞋已獲得 Trail Runner 的編輯選擇獎和 Outside Magazine 出品的年度齒輪標題"
